name: Hijack
overview: When Flight KA29 is hijacked during its seven-hour journey from Dubai to London, Sam Nelson—an accomplished corporate negotiator—tries using his professional skills to save everyone on board. Will this high-risk strategy be his undoing?
tagline: Let them think they're in control.

episodes.name: Final Call
episodes.overview: Sam Nelson gets on a flight to London hoping to win back his ex-wife, but something on board feels wrong—and his suspicions are confirmed.

episodes.name: 3 Degrees
episodes.overview: Spotting an opportunity, Sam executes a plan to get a covert message to authorities on the ground.

episodes.name: Draw a Blank
episodes.overview: As the UK’s counterterrorism unit learns of Flight KA29, Sam gets involved in a risky plan to take on the hijackers.

episodes.name: Not Responding
episodes.overview: An incident team in Westminster scrambles to intercept fighter jets. Sam tries contacting the ground once more when a hijacker is injured.

episodes.name: Less Than an Hour
episodes.overview: Sam attempts to convince the hijackers to land the plane. A list of demands reveals who’s behind the hijacking.

episodes.name: Comply Slowly
episodes.overview: Faced with an impossible decision, the passengers ready themselves for a fight.
